      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense. I think the issue might be that some of the timestamps are slightly off due to millisecond differences, so a standard join isn't catching them or it's causing duplicates. Do you have a way to do an \"as-of\" merge or some kind of fuzzy matching so I can join on the closest time instead of an exact match?",
